Class DataStorageAndOutputWorker

  • java.lang.Object
    • find_political_donors.DataStorageEngine.DataStorageAndOutputWorker
  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    public abstract class DataStorageAndOutputWorker
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Runnable
    This is an abstract class that defines a thread for storing data and output to files. The data will be read from a BlockingQueue.
